  shipit 1.0.0

    Ship an app

  USAGE

    shipit [command] [options] <app> [build]

  COMMANDS

    (default)     The default action, command is optional

  ARGUMENTS

    app       The app to deploy
    build     Which build to ship, dev or prod

  OPTIONS

    --delay, -d     How long to wait in seconds before shipping (default 0)

  BUILT-IN COMMANDS

    help        Display help for a command
    version     Display version

  BUILT-IN OPTIONS

    --help, -h        Display help
    --version, -v     Display version
    --no-color        Disable colors
    --quiet           Quiet mode - will only display warn and error messages
    --verbose         Verbose mode - will also display debug messages

